smaller Hollywood passages, treated with irony and a bit of exaggeration,
and then scenes from the CIA headquarters and other institutions with regular men discussing the situation around the conference tables, in the corridors and on the phone...
Ben Affleck has managed to relaunch his career in a remarkable way.
